snippet.title: Playing the Sonic 2 McDonalds Happy Meal Browser Game
snippet.description:
McDonalds made a Sonic 2 browser game with an augmented reality component. For more info, including on how to play the game, go here:

https://www.sonicstadium.org/2022/04/you-can-play-this-mcdonalds-sonic-2-browser-game-with-or-without-a-happy-meal/
